嘅時候好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我頭先著緊短袖"},{"pid":"15117eff88667817775ab035953254068578fb5b","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd5d2e09e76bfb66c4b7b03fb752e0570ddb763","tid":2497180,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陣間使唔使滑雪返落去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"有人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我着雪鞋行上嚟所以要行返落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f7865ceea5287a3ca96b4b457ff0a5381abfba","tid":2497180,"uid":332128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁偏僻都有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980b9b120878363115be5d1f6a28e313646260b","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"真點上到頂！原來呢個先係頂<br />\n（而家已經落埋山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdswbc36cr9hQ1GgiUNLGqnCBKYXxWVgNkDmMThmMthyo?filename=EtC4FCo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtC4FCo.png&h=354a94e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係到望到瑞典<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;-ikea肉丸<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb51W2YDJGcJYhD1BPuxChjCNxw4CnB6ug4gEoKV6ALGr?filename=BqTzipE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqTzipE.png&h=704a6179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說上山嘅時候爆林行小路，見到hare腳印<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZtEG1Zi4Wa85JsDQrTXJmoVrJEVyyTxsNwF5ct92DeQg?filename=WQqNDqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQqNDqe.png&h=6daa128e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狐狸腳印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一串咁好優雅<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfYRCFjUJFJBwiBeozdbY8fGMGRJpZGkjSJiAzaWEz9T5?filename=XLAYK5j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLAYK5j.png&h=f0a49cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有我嘅腳印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRD2F23pEpJj5c21PWMQ3nQniDwDbiAX7F6C77ZUYZCPh?filename=DT2sDqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT2sDqO.png&h=a6e3a5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落山決定行返大路落<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb3NmDfAc3kxSG5F5cJWfjXvpsTPWJFDppvtcdSd63F8U?filename=K6s8nSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6s8nSB.png&h=af0a3795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有蛋黃哥樣嘅山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcwBa9a38BWRiRT1hnS9Q1iVPmizMXzu5Ca42tSphQYfb?filename=Tqy7Drb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqy7Drb.png&h=129e53f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天使光環雲<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeU5iZAMGgypbj44Yq7JK58DboLgE1YfuRZFSLqPNrbaV?filename=WxhPRMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxhPRMc.png&h=10aaa0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魔鬼魚山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQbLsp1Ct56HdjSvcfWwmwb6h2Xeo5PHzfMgLwY9HMfTf?filename=WuYWwMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuYWwMd.png&h=52806ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安全落到山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmanLhFGzz5sn9QmGhyKxv3kcgQkhWb388ZoLrZzKEyhpK?filename=xAy7Dre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAy7Dre.png&h=f8b35e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人玩滑翔傘！應該係 我都想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3e4KZV7hbkz9CVY1DycoVkukLKhZPx3ijWmSccqsng1?filename=8EEOnSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EEOnSV.png&h=eac65a04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a5fc5352b2a7adbdf1c04e8ef6deb7502eec92e","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b0f7865ceea5287a3ca96b4b457ff0a5381abfba","tid":2497180,"uid":332128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁偏僻都有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"Yes芬蘭網絡覆蓋率差唔多100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828d6f8d85b78416ac0a4071edf94461e3c114d8","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbjLWFnuXpQ2TotK28CEc7FqKM9fXJwEhZhzh3dTRmL1M?filename=VPJO7nK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPJO7nK.png&h=0bfda4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成！！總共行咗12k，用咗六個鐘，郊遊速度加埋休息食嘢影相都算輕鬆行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲意猶未盡，可能今晚再去行吓第二座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家要焗桑拿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50750a5113aaee4fc95c04b84732962559ab14b2","tid":2497180,"uid":303821,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"好正，好想去外國行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb598e2c57206bd657fa5df44be305e69613ae16","tid":2497180,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"想試下行雪山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3892efc0cd1177d8244ff1ae36eb080ffd9da21","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"傍晚嘅時候又上多次山睇日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留咗係山兩個鐘諗住睇極光 但唔好彩佢哋無出現到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRSEjJtMSajL58FkTtzwZx18PobLnefADeJCdGk68ipKP?filename=2t9Saic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2t9Saic.jpg&h=9d166a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY36tQDotjLPWBBhSUfdpSmuDy4r8jYNDH7HA2EzFWWbZ?filename=1ebpLRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ebpLRz.jpg&h=af42dbb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a3f3c9fe011f128817abcfd019c8b38d09018d2","tid":2497180,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4eb8db691a22512a91244c8fe6d1a4a38a6a6ab5","tid":2497180,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"巴打幾好想像力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa910286e4eea6d9f7c867f02816b58d9539dce7","tid":2497180,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"雪山都收到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕唔怕死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871f3d86a99ae5a2a4632131e04db92ed6ed1d9e","tid":2497180,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34d7494f3a3065453addbc25c64ecda36c57872","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"上到頂了wuwu 好宏偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uf6w3EM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUf6w3EM.png&h=acc9606e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐低食個bell<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Spdzg8t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpdzg8t.png&h=70ac91ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"好似幾好食"},{"pid":"f66902a20374b393317278d3b2d697d692aad3fd","tid":2497180,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45c250280f8540a9976c9eb30a7ddd6f7c958157","tid":2497180,"uid":31962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"一人之境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我怕凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"運動緊其實唔凍<br />\n屌你老味第一次去滑雪著得多衫得滯焗到成身濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671d73a9cc0bc3ef6c3451939e765def4608faa8","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa910286e4eea6d9f7c867f02816b58d9539dce7","tid":2497180,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"雪山都收到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕唔怕死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"發射塔就係對面山個頂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋芬蘭網絡覆蓋率差唔多100%！<br />\n唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩係好天氣 同埋啲trails有曬mark唔怕當失路"},{"pid":"eed3b98fd504ecdc689917e2f7dd2fce223351e7","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb598e2c57206bd657fa5df44be305e69613ae16","tid":2497180,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"想試下行雪山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"好正 行上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca2a7a8ac0ad966aed3f4d9d162a268715bb989","tid":2497180,"uid":161569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"行幾耐？"},{"pid":"578f3804a57740bd2d742d1c89560cdf10512570","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4eb8db691a22512a91244c8fe6d1a4a38a6a6ab5","tid":2497180,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"巴打幾好想像力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"一個人行係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bf1e781157bc2b53057838e5fa125a0987aff3","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca2a7a8ac0ad966aed3f4d9d162a268715bb989","tid":2497180,"uid":161569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"行幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"一日行一座左右"},{"pid":"c97b1ed67d506a541777fdaa98e5dd6f14c77e31","tid":2497180,"uid":304684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"令我回想起早幾年喺奧地利行雪山，喺Alps山腳留咗一段腳印，已經心滿意足了"},{"pid":"86865056280cccc4a66f73cfcbac8ed7cf2a96c3","tid":2497180,"uid":27978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"好chill呀"},{"pid":"62a0d54e39e80fa27943962dd55719251bb22e0e","tid":2497180,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"一個人行唔怕死左無人知?"},{"pid":"99c124a3c0996c17ae5903f85dd1790083f50f42","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"今日join個skiing tour去個遠少少叫Ailakkaj&auml;rvi嘅湖<br />\nJoin tour因為無試過back country skiing同今日天氣都幾差<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係酒店食個雪山景早餐～全部都係berries<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUtCNQGio3Td1XMqLetReonBHJ5U2Ah5DCz5crJ2wnBd2?filename=g13jCJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg13jCJO.png&h=049c62b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完就起行 my導遊Gareth同佢隻狗Aapeli <br />\nGareth係Kiwi但搬咗嚟呢到十年 佢專搞啲成個禮拜嘅skiing tour/hiking tour<br />\nAapeli係一團毛球 我分唔到佢塊面同pat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRn1w7xmNrcnSPfVrf1ZAnfdbnmCFuqyEXJbbTMwjHHPH?filename=XUkFnbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUkFnbD.png&h=5f85a753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPJowFpHHuLdSLLdsXpfVqCi5UccS1agegeuBCnu5Fp5m?filename=FZF2Axk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZF2Axk.png&h=ba5700a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔食得嘅核突fungus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmct67cWytyydD8AEcCaq6u4zA6JTedUbjGYXDkxEjgr4h?filename=TiSTHb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTiSTHb3.png&h=e8dab444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日天氣麻麻地 間唔落幾大雪搞到成身濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但白茫茫一片都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmevA8kHYFYqsSo8oFEkaCtXfmHNeNJHq8FZicc5CDPJUG?filename=79zfa64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79zfa64.png&h=72410b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n穿過咗森林後見到好多隻reindeer！！順帶一提芬蘭無野生reindeer 全部都係有人養的<br />\n係Lapland嘅supermarket可以買到reindeer肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX7suXH6oed553XbhBVgVdNEyENyoYm3T4vzdfKw7TUeB?filename=xjebtUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjebtUZ.png&h=7e7157f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇完reindeer之後能見度急降 我諗應該得返20米到 但好彩就嚟到呢個湖邊嘅hut <br />\n個hut好well constructed有火爐有柴有枱櫈 仲有木牀<br />\n去到呢到ski咗7公里到 停低飲杯熱豬食個lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWqSnRFBto9ywvUGB4K3TJgUNfn5LwiBSymkFdYcGNj5m?filename=eBk2AA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBk2AA2.png&h=ab336c63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5UFn5zYvoMNfEmczcg8kVYcfDewLC9rGBLt8nh194vx?filename=D7VNMHO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD7VNMHO.png&h=a3f71f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有趣嘅留言簿 我都留咗字 睇吓會唔會有香港人去睇吓我寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfLq7df5XQH35NTm44pm82n4vhk2tG4pEDTykeqAY8NEa?filename=zMBM2ie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMBM2ie.png&h=2f93926f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旱廁 想講佢係無味嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfHvNipW62yB4CNbvXLEv7Vioe5KojtU1xfUYJEXHvCZ3?filename=vVDLypZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVDLypZ.png&h=42cf29b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抖夠就返去了~ 停咗雪睇到風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTx618xT4VM6U4w5E5hq1u6shusvU83q7wNJ2GeMHsJDK?filename=jDyLyrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDyLyrm.png&h=f1abd26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQyo1P9B71TFCuhSQY1VnCmcitphrzWPNBpA8MwCtMmSW?filename=p68fVEM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp68fVEM.png&h=5d03468b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過條溪直接用kuksa裝水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別甜呀啲水<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeNTBLXuhC4rhSgL2nqXWMezmB2qAWA9qUd6aLcon7kdp?filename=moeCpyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoeCpyc.png&h=31f17f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就是這樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總共ski咗14k 用咗六個鐘 <br />\n第一次ski又唔好天算係咁吧 <br />\n平時係街見到人滑雪好似好輕鬆咁 但其實好攰好攰 尤其係森林入面啲雪好鬆 會成個人陷咗入啲雪到 <br />\n失平衡仆街一次仲攰過ski一公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但點都好都係挑戰自己嘅一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家成身散了 it&rsquo;s sauna time!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVPKe4NQJ4C2PV2KTykKQvaqHpa7y2VXeYqhMnYC8MYMx?filename=riTPfLd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FriTPfLd.jpg&h=20e485b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27974d26c07b97e8508825a70df253511543538d","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62a0d54e39e80fa27943962dd55719251bb22e0e","tid":2497180,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"一個人行唔怕死左無人知?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"日日都有人行嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋死係到都值"},{"pid":"41a48514ce6e8a64bc79e59e2f484eb4aa21f105","tid":2497180,"uid":287551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"芬蘭雪境真係好靚，一個人真係靜到可以聽到自己呼吸聲，啲空氣好似停左咁，有小小中二病但真係好舒服<br />\n利申早幾年去過kiilop&auml;&auml; cross country skiing<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmThTWGwoU4E1PawaVFnuemGjyjrVoe86K5nEpLd9FQA8U?filename=RqbUrXr.jpg\" data-thum